author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Mustek Says HY HEPS Expected To Be At Least 20% Higher Than Prior Period
text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - Mustek Ltd:
* HY ‍NET ASSET VALUE PER SHARE IS EXPECTED TO BE BETWEEN 1 265 CENTS AND 1 275 CENTS, COMPARED TO 1 067,57 CENTS AS AT 31 DECEMBER 2016​
* HY HEPS AND BASIC EPS ARE EXPECTED TO BE AT LEAST 20% HIGHER THAN HEPS OF 37,34 CENTS AND BASIC EPS OF 37,24 CENTS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
